text: Pfäffikon is the capital of the municipality of Freienbach, in Höfe District in the canton of Schwyz in Switzerland. It is the third biggest town of the canton after Küssnacht and Einsiedeln. == Other websites == * Pfaeffikon-SZ * Municipality of Pfäffikon Category:Villages in Schwyz Category:Höfe District
